<p>Here I have a small snippet which has a variable num_cpu under a if condition, i am not able to access it outside the if condition tag. How do i solve this?</p>  <p>How do i make the num_cpu global so that i can use it multiple times outside the for loop?</p>  <pre><code>    &lt;xsl:for-each select="t:container"&gt;         &lt;xsl:if test="@name = 'cpu'"&gt;             &lt;xsl:variable name="num_cpu" select="t:leaf/t:value/@value"/&gt;        &lt;/xsl:if&gt;        &lt;xsl:value-of select="$num_cpu"/&gt;     &lt;/xsl:for-each&gt; </code></pre>